Class HabitEventHistory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301f17t11.cupofjava.Models.HabitEventHistory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class HabitEventHistory
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Handles the list of habit events being displayed. It shows the habit events in reverse chronological order so the user can see the most recent habit event at the top.
